				<div itemprop="commentText" class='post entry-content '>
					Yes.  You need to prefix it with the table name you want to pull the field from.  That would be the Jobs table in this case, so:<br /><pre class='prettyprint lang-auto linenums:0'>
SELECT
                Jobs.JobNumber,
                MAX(PostDate) as postDate
FROM Jobs
LEFT JOIN Posts ON Posts.JobNumber=Jobs.JobNumber
GROUP BY
                Jobs.JobNumber
ORDER BY
                postDate
</pre>
					
					<br />
					
				</div>
				
				
